# Binary files must never be processed as text. External tooling (AI Studio)
# has repeatedly corrupted images and jars by round-tripping them through a
# text encoder; marking them binary tells git (and well-behaved tools) to keep
# their bytes exactly as-is - no EOL conversion, no charset re-encoding.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.jar binary
*.wav binary
*.mp3 binary
*.ogg binary
*.keystore binary
*.jks binary
